            "title": "銀價突破100美元創新高　金價破頂迫近5000美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15607940&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">黃金及白銀價格再創新高，經濟及政治局勢不確定，資金流入避險資產。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨白銀價格突破每盎司100美元關口，曾觸及約102.85美元，升約7%，今年以來不足1個月時間累計升約44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價迫近每盎司5000美元關口，現貨金高見4989.61美元，升近1.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期金2月合約高見4991.4美元，收報4979.7美元，升66.3美元，升幅1.3%，本周累計升逾8%。</p>\n</div>",
