            "title": "歐股低收　德股本周跌約1.6%　結束8星期升勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15607932&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲股市普遍向下，市場持續評估格陵蘭問題引發的歐美貿易緊張局勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐盟執委會擬將對美國總額達930億歐元的報復性貿易措施暫緩期再延長6個月。另外，德國總理默茨表示，不能接受美國總統特朗普倡議的和平委員會，目前的設立形式。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利及西班牙股市跌幅較大，跌約0.6%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英法股市連升兩日後回軟，富時100指數收報10143點，跌6點；法國CAC指數收報8143點，跌5點，兩者都跌約0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數反覆向上，25000點關口阻力仍大，收報24900點，升44點，升幅約0.2%，連升兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德股本周累計跌約1.6%，結束8個星期升勢。英股跌0.9%，亦結束3星期升勢。法股跌1.4%，連跌兩星期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15607932-%e6%ad%90%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e3%80%80%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%841-6%e3%80%80%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f8%e6%98%9f%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%87%e5%8b%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:27:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
